Books are a great way for improving self and becoming more knowledgeable. Self help books are good for if you need a bit of motivation
and help. Here are ten good self help books that are a must read. 1. The Alchemist by Paulo Coelho  2. The 7 Habits of Highly Effective People by Stephen R. Covey  3. The Power of Now by Eckhart Tolle  4. Rich Dad, Poor Dad by Robert Kiyosaki  5. The Road Less Traveled by M Scott Peck  6. Man’s Search for Meaning by Victor Frankl  7. The Power of Positive Thinking by Norman Vincent Peale  8. The Science of Getting Rich by Wallace D. Wattles  9. How to Win Friends and Influence People by Dale Carnegie  10. The secret by Rhonda Byrne 